Empty library instruction :
If you just clone emty_library repository, remove the git folder and create a new one for your project :
$ rm -rf .git
$ git init
$ git remote add origin git@address:project/repository.git
You can now delete this section from the README file.

Project Target

Create build directory:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build

Build project:
$ cmake ..
$ make -j 3

To accelerate the process, use release version
$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
$ make -j 3

Install:
$ make
$ make install
or
$ sudo make install

Create documentation:
$ make doc
$ firefox ./doc/html/index.html &

Create tests:
$ cmake -DENABLE_TEST=ON ..
$ make
$ make test
